Classes used when making searches on the map.

    CostDecider
    Determines the cost of a single move.
    GoalDecider
    Used by Map.search(net.sf.freecol.common.model.Unit, net.sf.freecol.common.model.Location, net.sf.freecol.common.model.pathfinding.GoalDecider, net.sf.freecol.common.model.pathfinding.CostDecider, int, net.sf.freecol.common.model.Unit, net.sf.freecol.common.util.LogBuilder) in order to determine a goal.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CostDeciders
    Cost deciders to be used while finding paths.
    GoalDeciders
    Handy library of GoalDeciders.
    GoalDeciders.MultipleAdjacentDecider
    A class to wrap a goal decider that searches for paths to an adjacent tile to a set of locations, and the results of such a search.

Package net.sf.freecol.common.model.pathfinding Description

Classes used when making searches on the map.

The classes in this package is used by the search and findPath methods in Map.
